Tokens - Enum in lexer
This file is automatically generated
- it contains the enumberation of all of the tokens
tokens - Static variable in class lexer.TokenType
 
TokenSetup - Class in lexer.setup
TokenSetup class is used to read the tokens from file tokens and automatically build the 2 classes/files TokenType.java and Sym.java
Therefore, if there is any change to the tokens then we only need to modify the file tokens and run this program again before using the compiler

it contains the table of mappings from token constants to their Symbols
